[Guest 1]: So that thing that you say, but there is a, you know, I will not name this person, a very

00:32:35.100 --> 00:32:41.340
[Guest 1]: smart alecky media commentator, stroke, you know, he writes and talks about the media

00:32:41.340 --> 00:32:48.180
[Guest 1]: all over the place, very hip, very, this one said I was at some meeting to audience of

