[Guest 1]: And you know, I can kind of break it down and rubbish it.

00:33:04.420 --> 00:33:10.340
[Guest 1]: But basically, what I'm trying to say, filtration in a newspaper is critical, but it was not

00:33:10.340 --> 00:33:11.340
[Guest 1]: a dialogue.

