[Guest 1]: Letters to the editor and which got cut.

00:33:14.700 --> 00:33:19.760
[Guest 1]: And very few people, papers really give it much thought was no dialogue.

00:33:19.760 --> 00:33:24.420
[Guest 1]: You didn't like a piece, you lumped it, Twitter has no dialogue.

